   "source": [
    "&nbsp;\n",
    "## 1.1 鐢≧MSNorm灞傛浛鎹ayerNorm灞俓n",
    "\n",
    "- 棣栧厛锛岀敤鍧囨柟鏍瑰眰褰掍竴鍖栵紙RMSNorm锛夋浛鎹ayerNorm\n",
    "- LayerNorm浣跨敤鍧囧€煎拰鏂瑰樊褰掍竴鍖栬緭鍏ワ紝鑰孯MSNorm浠呬娇鐢ㄥ潎鏂规牴锛岃繖鎻愰珮浜嗚绠楁晥鐜嘰n",
    "- RMSNorm鎿嶄綔濡備笅锛屽叾涓?x$鏄緭鍏ワ紝$\\gamma$鏄彲璁粌鍙傛暟锛堝悜閲忥級锛?\\epsilon$鏄竴涓皬甯告暟锛岀敤浜庨伩鍏嶉浂闄ら敊璇細\n",
    "\n",
    "$$y_i = \\frac{x_i}{\\text{RMS}(x)} \\gamma_i, \\quad \\text{鍏朵腑} \\quad \\text{RMS}(x) = \\sqrt{\\epsilon + \\frac{1}{n} \\sum x_i^2}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "- 鏇村璇︽儏锛岃鍙傞槄璁烘枃[Root Mean Square Layer Normalization (2019)](https://arxiv.org/abs/1910.07467)\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "import torch.nn as nn"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "#####################################\n",
    "# Chapter 4\n",
    "#####################################\n",
    "\n",
    "# class LayerNorm(nn.Module):\n",
    "#     def __init__(self, emb_dim: int) -> None:\n",
    "#         super().__init__()\n",
    "#         self.eps = 1e-5\n",
    "#         self.scale = nn.Parameter(torch.ones(emb_dim))\n",
    "#         self.shift = nn.Parameter(torch.zeros(emb_dim))\n",
    "\n",
    "#     def forward(self, x: torch.Tensor) -> torch.Tensor:\n",
    "#         mean = x.mean(dim=-1, keepdim=True)\n",
    "#         var = x.var(dim=-1, keepdim=True, unbiased=False)\n",
    "#         norm_x = (x - mean) / torch.sqrt(var + self.eps)\n",
    "#         return self.scale * norm_x + self.shift\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "class RMSNorm(nn.Module):\n",
    "    def __init__(self, emb_dim: int, eps: float = 1e-5) -> None:\n",
    "        super().__init__()\n",
    "        self.eps = eps\n",
    "        self.emb_dim = emb_dim\n",
    "        self.weight = nn.Parameter(torch.ones(emb_dim)).float()\n",
    "\n",
    "    def forward(self, x: torch.Tensor) -> torch.Tensor:\n",
    "        means = x.pow(2).mean(dim=-1, keepdim=True)\n",
    "        x_normed = x * torch.rsqrt(means + self.eps)\n",
    "        return (x_normed * self.weight).to(dtype=x.dtype)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "- 浠ヤ笅浠ｇ爜cell鏍￠獙涓婅堪瀹炵幇鍜宼orch鍐呯疆瀹炵幇鏄惁鐩稿悓"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "torch.manual_seed(123)\n",
    "\n",
    "example_batch = torch.randn(2, 3, 4)  # 闅忔満鐢熸垚涓€涓?x3x4鐨則ensor\n",
    "\n",
    "rms_norm = RMSNorm(emb_dim=example_batch.shape[-1])  # 鍒涘缓RMSNorm瀹炰緥\n",
    "rmsnorm_pytorch = torch.nn.RMSNorm(example_batch.shape[-1], eps=1e-5)  # 鍒涘缓torch.nn.RMSNorm瀹炰緥\n",
    "\n",
    "assert torch.allclose(rms_norm(example_batch), rmsnorm_pytorch(example_batch))  # 鏍￠獙涓や釜瀹炰緥鐨勮緭鍑烘槸鍚︾浉鍚?
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "&nbsp;\n",
    "## 1.2 鐢⊿iLU婵€娲诲嚱鏁版浛鎹ELU婵€娲诲嚱鏁癨n",
    "\n",
    "- Llama浣跨敤SiLU婵€娲诲嚱鏁帮紙鑰屼笉鏄疓ELU锛夛紝瀹冧篃琚О涓篠wish鍑芥暟锛歕n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\text{silu}(x) = x \\cdot \\sigma(x), \\quad \\text{鍏朵腑} \\quad \\sigma(x) \\text{ 鏄痩ogistic sigmoid鍑芥暟銆倉\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "- 鏈夊叧鏇村淇℃伅锛岃鍙傞槄SiLU璁烘枃锛歔Sigmoid-Weighted Linear Units for Neural Network Function Approximation in Reinforcement Learning (2017)](https://arxiv.org/abs/1702.03118)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "#####################################\n",
    "# Chapter 4\n",
    "#####################################\n",
    "\n",
    "# class GELU(nn.Module):\n",
    "#     def __init__(self) -> None:\n",
    "#         super().__init__()\n",
    "\n",
    "#     def forward(self, x: torch.Tensor) -> torch.Tensor:\n",
    "#         return 0.5 * x * (1 + torch.tanh(\n",
    "#             torch.sqrt(torch.tensor(2.0 / torch.pi)) *\n",
    "#             (x + 0.044715 * torch.pow(x, 3))\n",
    "#         ))\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "class SiLU(nn.Module):\n",
    "    def __init__(self) -> None:\n",
    "        super(SiLU, self).__init__()\n",
    "\n",
    "    def forward(self, x: torch.Tensor) -> torch.Tensor:\n",
    "        return x * torch.sigmoid(x)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "silu = SiLU()\n",
    "\n",
    "assert torch.allclose(silu(example_batch), torch.nn.functional.silu(example_batch))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "&nbsp;\n",
    "## 1.3 鏇存柊FeedForward灞俓n",
    "\n",
    "- 瀹為檯涓婏紝Llama浣跨敤浜嗕竴绉嶇О涓篠wiGLU鐨凷iLU鐨刓"闂ㄦ帶绾挎€у崟鍏僜"(GLU)鍙樹綋锛岃繖鍩烘湰涓婂鑷翠簡涓€涓粨鏋勭暐鏈変笉鍚岀殑`FeedForward`妯″潡\n",
    "- SwiGLU鍦ㄥ墠棣堝眰涓娇鐢ㄩ棬鎺ф満鍒讹紝鍏紡涓猴細\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\text{SwiGLU}(x) = \\text{SiLU}(\\text{Linear}_1(x)) * \\text{Linear}_2(x)$$\n",
    "\n",
    "- 杩欓噷锛?\\text{Linear}_1$鍜?\\text{Linear}_2$鏄袱涓嚎鎬у眰锛?*$琛ㄧず鍏冪礌绾т箻娉昞n",
    "- 绗笁涓嚎鎬у眰$\\text{Linear}_3$鍦ㄨ繖涓棬鎺ф縺娲讳箣鍚庡簲鐢╘n",
    "\n",
    "- 鏈夊叧鏇村淇℃伅锛岃鍙傞槄SwiGLU璁烘枃锛歔GLU Variants Improve Transformer (2020)](https://arxiv.org/abs/2002.05202)\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "#####################################\n",
    "# Chapter 4\n",
    "#####################################\n",
    "# class FeedForward(nn.Module):\n",
    "#     def __init__(self, cfg) -> None:\n",
    "#         super().__init__()\n",
    "#         self.layers = nn.Sequential(\n",
    "#             nn.Linear(cfg[\"emb_dim\"], 4 * cfg[\"emb_dim\"]),\n",
    "#             GELU(),\n",
    "#             nn.Linear(4 * cfg[\"emb_dim\"], cfg[\"emb_dim\"]),\n",
    "#         )\n",
    "\n",
    "#     def forward(self, x: torch.Tensor) -> torch.Tensor:\n",
    "#         return self.layers(x)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "class FeedForward(nn.Module):\n",
    "    def __init__(self, cfg) -> None:\n",
    "        super().__init__()\n",
    "        self.fc1 = nn.Linear(cfg[\"emb_dim\"], cfg[\"hidden_dim\"], dtype=cfg[\"dtype\"], bias=False)\n",
    "        self.fc2 = nn.Linear(cfg[\"emb_dim\"], cfg[\"hidden_dim\"], dtype=cfg[\"dtype\"], bias=False)\n",
    "        self.fc3 = nn.Linear(cfg[\"hidden_dim\"], cfg[\"emb_dim\"], dtype=cfg[\"dtype\"], bias=False)\n",
    "        self.silu = SiLU()\n",
    "\n",
    "    def forward(self, x: torch.Tensor) -> torch.Tensor:\n",
    "        x_fc1 = self.fc1(x)\n",
    "        x_fc2 = self.fc2(x)\n",
    "        x = self.silu(x_fc1) * x_fc2\n",
    "        return self.fc3(x)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "&nbsp;\n",
    "## 1.4 瀹炵幇RoPE\n",
    "\n",
    "- 鍦℅PT妯″瀷涓紝浣嶇疆宓屽叆鏄涓嬪疄鐜扮殑锛歕n",
    "\n",
    "```python\n",
    "self.pos_emb = nn.Embedding(cfg[\"context_length\"], cfg[\"emb_dim\"])\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "- 涓庝紶缁熺殑缁濆浣嶇疆宓屽叆涓嶅悓锛孡lama浣跨敤鏃嬭浆浣嶇疆宓屽叆(RoPE)锛岃繖浣垮畠鑳藉鍚屾椂鎹曡幏缁濆鍜岀浉瀵逛綅缃俊鎭痋n",
    "- RoPE鐨勫弬鑰冭鏂囨槸[RoFormer: Enhanced Transformer with Rotary Position Embedding (2021)](https://arxiv.org/abs/2104.09864)\n",
    "- RoPE鏈変袱绉嶇瓑浠风殑瀹炵幇鏂瑰紡锛氬垎鍗婄増鏈拰浜ら敊鍋舵暟/濂囨暟鐗堟湰锛涘彧瑕佷竴鑷村湴閰嶅缁村害骞朵娇鐢ㄧ浉鍚岀殑浣欏鸡/姝ｅ鸡椤哄簭锛屽畠浠湪鏁板涓婃槸鐩稿悓鐨勶紙鏈夊叧鏇村淇℃伅锛岃鍙傞槄姝GitHub璁ㄨ](https://github.com/rasbt/LLMs-from-scratch/issues/751)锛塡n",
    "- 杩欐浠ｇ爜浣跨敤浜嗕笌Hugging Face transformers锛圼modeling_llama.py](https://github.com/huggingface/transformers/blob/e42587f596181396e1c4b63660abf0c736b10dae/src/transformers/models/llama/modeling_llama.py#L173-L188)锛夌被浼肩殑RoPE鍒嗗崐鏂规硶銆俓n",
    "- 鐒惰€岋紝鍘熷鐨凴oPE璁烘枃鍜孧eta鐨勫畼鏂筁lama 2浠撳簱浣跨敤浜ら敊锛堝伓鏁?濂囨暟锛夌増鏈紙[llama/model.py](https://github.com/meta-llama/llama/blob/6c7fe276574e78057f917549435a2554000a876d/llama/model.py#L64-L74)锛夛紱浣嗗鍓嶆墍杩帮紝瀹冧滑鏄瓑浠风殑"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def precompute_rope_params(head_dim, theta_base=10_000, context_length=4096):\n",
    "    assert head_dim % 2 == 0, \"Embedding dimension must be even\"\n",
    "\n",
    "    # 璁＄畻閫嗛鐜嘰n",
    "    inv_freq = 1.0 / (theta_base ** (torch.arange(0, head_dim, 2)[: (head_dim // 2)].float() / head_dim))\n",
    "\n",
    "    # 鐢熸垚浣嶇疆绱㈠紩\n",
    "    positions = torch.arange(context_length)\n",
    "\n",
    "    # 璁＄畻瑙掑害\n",
    "    angles = positions.unsqueeze(1) * inv_freq.unsqueeze(0)  # Shape: (context_length, head_dim // 2)\n",
    "\n",
    "    # 鎷撳睍瑙掑害閫傞厤head_dim\n",
    "    angles = torch.cat([angles, angles], dim=1)  # Shape: (context_length, head_dim)\n",
    "\n",
    "    # 棰勮绠梥ine鍜宑osine\n",
    "    cos = torch.cos(angles)\n",
    "    sin = torch.sin(angles)\n",
    "\n",
    "    return cos, sin\n",
    "\n",
    "def compute_rope(x, cos, sin):\n",
    "    # x: (batch_size, num_heads, seq_len, head_dim)\n",
    "    batch_size, num_heads, seq_len, head_dim = x.shape\n",
    "    assert head_dim % 2 == 0, \"Head dimension must be even\"\n",
    "\n",
    "    # 灏唜鍒嗗壊涓哄墠鍚庝袱閮ㄥ垎\n",
    "    x1 = x[..., : head_dim // 2]  # First half\n",
    "    x2 = x[..., head_dim // 2 :]  # Second half\n",
    "\n",
    "    # 鍙彇搴忓垪闀垮害\n",
    "    cos = cos[:seq_len, :].unsqueeze(0).unsqueeze(0)  # Shape: (1, 1, seq_len, head_dim)\n",
    "    sin = sin[:seq_len, :].unsqueeze(0).unsqueeze(0)\n",
    "\n",
    "    # 搴旂敤鏃嬭浆鍙樻崲\n",
    "    rotated = torch.cat((-x2, x1), dim=-1)\n",
    "    x_rotated = (x * cos) + (rotated * sin)\n",
    "\n",
    "    return x_rotated.to(dtype=x.dtype)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "- 浠ヤ笅鏄皢RoPE搴旂敤浜巂q`鍜宍k`寮犻噺鐨勭ず渚?
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Settings\n",
    "batch_size = 2\n",
    "context_len = 5\n",
    "num_heads = 4\n",
    "head_dim = 16\n",
    "\n",
    "# 鍒濆鍖朢oPE鍙傛暟\n",
    "cos, sin = precompute_rope_params(head_dim=head_dim, context_length=context_len)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 闅忔満鍒涘缓queries鍜宬eys\n",
    "torch.manual_seed(123)\n",
    "queries = torch.randn(batch_size, num_heads, context_len, head_dim)\n",
    "keys = torch.randn(batch_size, num_heads, context_len, head_dim)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 搴旂敤鏃嬭浆浣嶇疆缂栫爜\n",
    "queries_rot = compute_rope(queries, cos, sin)\n",
    "keys_rot = compute_rope(keys, cos, sin)"
